T02D2808:165a-0: @165a * // 'phags pa thugs rje chen po longs spyod mi zad pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2808:165a-1: re zhig sgrub pa po 'byor pa dman pa dang /
T02D2808:165a-2: phun sum tshogs pa rgud pas zil gyis non te bag zhum pa dang /
T02D2808:165a-3: yod kyang myur du 'dzad pas ma rungs par byed pa de dag thams cad /
T02D2808:165a-4: chags pa dang brnab sems kyis rang dang gzhan gyis
T02D2808:165a-5: yongs su bzung ba la mngon par gdung ba spangs
T02D2808:165a-6: te / 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs rgya mtsho'i gter gyi bdag po la skyabs su dong bar bya'o //
T02D2808:165a-8: n'il rin chen las grub pa'i //
T02D2808:165a-9: gzhal med khang mchog dbus su ni //
T02D2808:165a-10: mgon po longs spyod mi zad bsgom //
T02D2808:165a-11: gser gyi bum pa bzad bkang pa //
T02D2808:165a-12: nor bu tshom tshom skyug pa'i kha //
T02D2808:165a-13: dpag bsam shing chen rgyas pa'i gseb //
T02D2808:165a-14: sprin grib la ni yongs su rtsen //
T02D2808:165a-15: g-yas dmar g-yon sngo dbus dkar zhal //
T02D2808:165a-16: snang mtha' rdo rje thig les brgyan //
T02D2808:165a-17: nor sbyin byin rlob skyabs mdzad dang //
T02D2808:165a-18: gter dang lcags kyu padmo'i phyag / skyil krung phyed
T02D2808:165a-19: brten kun da'i mdog /'dom gang 'od gsal 'khor lo
T02D2808:165a-20: sogs // rin chen bdun 'dzag mu tig 'bru'i //
T02D2808:165a-21: char 'bebs g-yo ba mi mnga' ba'o //
T02D2808:165a-22: de yi phyag rgya nor sbyin par mdzad pa'i bdud rtsi can gyi mthong thos las /
T02D2808:165a-23: nor bu dang 'bru dang sman gyi char dod tshe
T02D2808:165a-24: brtsegs pa lta bu rgyun ma chad par 'ongs pas
T02D2808:165a-25: bdag gi longs spyod thams cad kyi sbubs su 'jug
T02D2808:165a-26: par bya'o // aom a'a:hr'i:shr'i a'ary'a wa lo ki te
T02D2808:165a-27: shva ra ma ma sarba si bho ga ratna ratne
T02D2808:165a-28: par bya'o // / ma h'a tsinta ma ni dha
T02D2808:165a-29: ra dha ra aa ksha ya aa kshmoo pa tisthati
T02D2808:165a-30: par bya'o // / h'um / bdag nyid btsun mo
T02D2808:165b-0: padmo can @165b gyi ting nge 'dzin gyis me tog
T02D2808:165b-1: dmar po dang dkar po sil ma thogs la /
T02D2808:165b-2: pog phor bdug cing thal mo sbyar ba'am /
T02D2808:165b-3: 'dud pa sngon du song bas mchod par bya'o //
T02D2808:165b-4: de nas ji tsam longs spyod pas zad pa de tsam 'phags pa'i phyag nas blang ngo //
T02D2808:165b-5: bla ma dang lha mchod pa dang phan pa'i gnas dang /
T02D2808:165b-6: mgon med pa la sbyin pa'i rim pa lhag pa'i
T02D2808:165b-7: bsam pa dang ma dral ba ni dam tshig go
T02D2808:165b-8: // grub pa'i 'bras bus lus can la /
T02D2808:165b-9: bsngo dang nga rgyal med nyid dang //
T02D2808:165b-10: byin pas dbul dang phongs 'gyur zhes //
T02D2808:165b-11: dogs bral de yis spyad mi bya //
